Riley?

26:16.884 --> 26:20.595
There's somethin' there.
l mean, that's real.

26:20.679 --> 26:24.515
lt's clean and simple,
and you got yourself
ahold of somethin'.

26:24.600 --> 26:27.810
That's what l was tryin'
to tell them clowns
in Nashville.

26:28.937 --> 26:30.438
