of "That'll Be The Day"
by Buddy Holly and the Crickets.

34:35.465 --> 34:38.842
And thank you
for calling me all the way
from Lubbock, Montana.

34:38.927 --> 34:43.514
No, that's Lubbock, Texas.
Uh, thanks a lot for playin' it.

34:43.598 --> 34:46.350
l appreciate it.
And tell the missus "hello."

34:46.434 --> 34:49.603
Thank you, Buddy!
