Keep the change.

36:25.325 --> 36:26.825
Hey, thanks a lot, buddy!

36:26.910 --> 36:29.286
No, no, he's Buddy.
Huh?

36:29.370 --> 36:31.997
Wacko con artist.
Wacko.

36:35.752 --> 36:39.213
