Thanks for coming in.

37:36.563 --> 37:39.398
Thanks for
puttin' out our record.
How about some champagne?

37:39.524 --> 37:41.984
Come on in, fellas.
Let me have some Coca-Cola.

37:42.110 --> 37:45.445
Champagne's good for me.
l'll have a Dr. Pepper.

37:47.532 --> 37:50.701
[ Door Closes ]
[ Chuckles ]

37:50.785 --> 37:53.871
l hope you fellas
understand we didn't mean
to release your record...

37:53.955 --> 37:58.208
without letting you know first,
but our A&R man liked it
so much he just put it on out.

37:58.334 --> 38:01.962
Well, l think it's nice to have
a hit record without a contract.
Yes.

38:02.046 --> 38:06.174
Well, that's one of
the reasons l wanted—
Oh. Thank you, Maria.

38:06.301 --> 38:09.011
That's all right.
We'll get it. Thank you.
[ Giggling ]

38:09.137 --> 38:11.597
Here, let me.
No calls, please.

38:11.681 --> 38:14.308
Whoo.
Hot number, huh?

38:14.434 --> 38:18.061
What's her name?
Her name is Maria.
Maria Elena Santiago.

38:19.105 --> 38:21.815
Her aunt is in charge of
our Latin-American division.

38:21.900 --> 38:23.942
She sure is pretty.

38:24.027 --> 38:27.404
You know, fellas, l—
Oh, thank you.

38:27.488 --> 38:30.157
